        <p class=\"recruit_message-text conts-flowAnime js-anime\">\n              <span>Be a Mover</span>\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"recruit_message-text conts-flowAnime js-anime\">\n              <span>時代をより豊かな未来へと</span><span>動かす存在へ。</span>\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"recruit_message-text conts-flowAnime js-anime\">\n              <span>デジタル技術を駆使して、</span><span>自らの手で、</span><br>\n              <span>未来の景色に</span><span>鮮やかな彩りをつけよう。</span>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"recruit_messageMover-inner\">\n            <h2 class=\"recruit_messageMover-title conts-flowAnime js-anime\">\n              <figure class=\"recruit_messageMover-title-imageTitle\">\n                <img src=\"../../assets/img/home/mover_title.svg\" alt=\"\">\n              </figure>\n              <video class=\"recruit_messageMover-title-video\" src=\"../../assets/img/common/movie/sample.mp4\" autoplay muted loop playsinline></video>\n              <span class=\"slash recruit_messageMover-slash js-anime\"></span>\n            </h2>\n            <div class=\"recruit_messageMover-messageInner\">\n              <div class=\"recruit_messageMover-subTitle\">\n                <div class=\"recruit_messageMover-subTitle-text js-anime\">時代は自ら動かない。<div class=\"contsBand-anime js-anime\"></div></div>\n                <div class=\"recruit_messageMover-subTitle-text js-anime\">意志ある人が動かしていく。<div class=\"contsBand-anime js-anime\"></div></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"link container\">\n      <div class=\"link-inner\">\n        <div class=\"link-list\">\n          <a href=\"../topmessage/\" class=\"link-item\">\n            <div class=\"link-itemBox\">\n              <span class=\"slash link-item-slash js-anime\"></span>\n              <p class=\"link-item_text conts-flowAnime js-anime\">トップメッセージ</p>\n            </div>\n            <figure class=\"lin